Release Notes for Version 3.12.5
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.12.5 is the 6th and final release in
the Errata Tool 3.12 development period. It closes [45 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

The primary new feature in this release of Errata Tool is support for
attaching docker images to advisories and pushing them to CDN. It also
includes multi-product mappings management, RPMDiff autowaive rule cloning, and
a number of other improvements and bug fixes.

